    </section>
</nav></header><main aria-label="main content"><div class="speakable">
      <b data-is-speakable>COVID-19 Death Rates Point To Racial, Urban-Rural Divisions</b>   <b data-is-speakable>The virus is disproportionately affecting people of color, primarily in densely populated cities. This is where the urban-rural rift also comes into play — and, consequently, a political one.</b>
</div>
<div id="wrapper">
      <header class="contentheader contentheader--one" data-metrics='{"category":"The Coronavirus Crisis"}' ><div class="branding branding--seamus">
